                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 8.279,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Justice Kagan has our opinion this morning in Case 126, on our original docket, Kansas v. Nebraska."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.279,
                        "stop": 248.764,
                        "byte_start": 0,
                        "byte_stop": 0,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15094,
                            "name": "Elena Kagan",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/elena_kagan",
                            "last_name": "Kagan",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2738,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 1281157200,
                                    "date_end": 0,
                                    "appointing_president": "Barack Obama",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2738"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32690,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 44456,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/elena-kagan-photo_0.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 1931,
                            "identifier": "elena_kagan"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 8.279,
                                "stop": 15.34,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "In this case Kansas and Nebraska ask us to settle a dispute over their rights to the waters of the Republican River."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 15.34,
                                "stop": 26.16,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Those two states have long been parties to a compact, an agreement, apportioning those waters between them, saying how much of the river each state can use each year."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 26.16,
                                "stop": 31.93,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That compact needed to be approved by Congress, and when it was it became federal law."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 31.93,
                                "stop": 41.748,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "A prior round of litigation about the meaning of the compact ended in a settlement, but implementing that settlement gave rise to further disputes."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 41.748,
                                "stop": 46.81,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "This Court has what\u0027s called original jurisdiction over disputes between states."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 46.81,
                                "stop": 52.288,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That means those cases come straight to us without going through any Lower Courts."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 52.288,
                                "stop": 61.602,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "What we usually do when we get one of these cases is to appoint a special master to hear evidence and give us a recommendation of how the suit should be resolved."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 61.602,
                                "stop": 67.775,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That\u0027s what we did here and today we affirm the master\u0027s recommendation on all counts."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 67.775,
                                "stop": 69.733,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "There are two main issues."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 69.733,
                                "stop": 73.811,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "The first concerns proper remedies for a compact violation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 73.811,
                                "stop": 85.543,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Everyone agrees that in the first years after the settlement Nebraska used more than its share of Republican River water and that it must pay for the damages Kansas incurred as a result."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 85.543,
                                "stop": 89.43,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "But the master recommended that Nebraska pay more on top of that."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 89.43,
                                "stop": 98.573,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That it do something called disgorge profits, meaning give back some of what it gained from its compact violation, even beyond what Kansas lost."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 98.573,
                                "stop": 101.408,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That\u0027s an unusual remedy for a contract breach."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 101.408,
                                "stop": 103.424,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "But today we approve it."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 103.424,
                                "stop": 109.785,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "We agree with the master that Nebraska\u0027s overuse of water was no mere accident or even negligence."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 109.785,
                                "stop": 121.883,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Rather, Nebraska recklessly disregarded Kansas\u0027 rights, refusing to cut back on its use of water, even when it became clear that would pose a significant risk of harm to Kansas."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 121.883,
                                "stop": 129.097,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "To deter that kind of misconduct in the future we decide that an extra award of damages is appropriate."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 129.097,
                                "stop": 142.883,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "The second main issue is whether we can modify a technical appendix to the settlement called the accounting procedures to ensure that it properly reflects the intent of the parties in entering into the compact and settlement."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 142.883,
                                "stop": 148.896,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Nebraska asked for that change going forward, and the master recommended we make it."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 148.896,
                                "stop": 155.03,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "The problem arises because the compact was supposed to apportion only water from the Republican River."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 155.03,
                                "stop": 160.752,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "No one intended that the state\u0027s use of other water from other rivers would be affected at all."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 160.752,
                                "stop": 172.574,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "But for various reasons the accounting procedures, which are supposed to be used to compute how much Republican River water the states use, end up counting some water from the Platte River."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 172.574,
                                "stop": 177.787,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "That means that each year Nebraska gets charged for some water it should get for free."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 177.787,
                                "stop": 181.735,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "The change the master proposed would prevent that from happening."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 181.735,
                                "stop": 184.885,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Again, this is an unusual contract remedy."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 184.885,
                                "stop": 191.498,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Normally Courts don\u0027t change any part of an agreement, even a technical part that parties have entered into."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 191.498,
                                "stop": 194.666,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "But we think it\u0027s right to make the modification here."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 194.666,
                                "stop": 205.587,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "It\u0027s clear that the parties did not mean for the accounting procedures to have this effect and it\u0027s clear that this unintended consequence distorts the apportionment that the parties did have in mind."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 205.587,
                                "stop": 214.845,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "In fact, unless corrected, the accounting procedures would violate the compact itself, and the compact, as I said earlier, is federal law."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 214.845,
                                "stop": 228.014,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Throughout this opinion we make clear that in exercising our original jurisdiction this Court will use the full range of its equitable powers to enforce the terms of an interstate compact."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 228.014,
                                "stop": 234.86,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "The Chief Justice and Justice Scalia have each filed opinions, concurring in part and dissenting in part."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 234.86,
                                "stop": 248.764,
                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Justice Thomas has filed an opinion, concurring in part and dissenting in part, in which Justices Scalia and Alito joined, and in which the Chief Justice joins as to Part 3."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
